Naive Bayes Spam Classifier Using MRJob/Pyspark

Combined 5 SMS and email datasets (Kaggle; V. Metsis, I. Androutsopoulos and G. Paliouras)
- Preprocessing
- Deleting unnecessary/Null entries
- Formatting feature and class labels
- Assigning IDs for data entries

Small Data
- 479 KB
- 13.4% Spam

Data Sources: 
https://www.kaggle.com/venky73/spam-mails-dataset
https://www.kaggle.com/uciml/sms-spam-collection-dataset
https://www.kaggle.com/adepvenugopal/detecting-sms-spam-using-machine-learning
http://www2.aueb.gr/users/ion/data/enron-spam/
https://www.kaggle.com/balakishan77/spam-or-ham-email-classification

